1 - From a Fresh Ubuntu 16.04
2 - Install apache
  sudo apt-get update
  sudo apt-get install apache2
3 - Create flder in /var/cgi-bin
4 - Apache reload
  service apache2 reload
  perlmaven.com/perl-cgi-script-with-apache2
5 - Instal cpan 
  $ cpan JSON  
